### Create a new score
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/scores
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "playerId": "{{playerId}}",
  "gameId": "{{gameId}}",
  "score": 100
}

### Get all scores
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/scores
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Update score by ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/scores/{{scoreId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "score": 150
}

### Delete score by ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/scores/{{scoreId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

